{"word":"ῥήγνυμι","slug":"ῥήγνυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ῥήγνυμι</el></b> [by-form of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ῥήσσω\">ῥήσσω</a></el>] ‘cause to come apart by application of force’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of external force, <b>rip apart <a href='B:470 7:6'>Mt 7:6</a>; tear <a href='B:490 5:6'>Lk 5:6</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of internal force, <b>burst</b> wine-skins <b><el>Μ</el>k <a href='B:490 2:22'>2:22</a>; <a href='B:490 5:37'>Lk 5:37</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><a href='B:470 9:17'>Mt 9:17</a>.</b> In <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense of forceful emotional expression <b>break out <a href='B:550 4:27'>Gal 4:27</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ῥῆγμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ῥηθείς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}